<li id="cite_note-17"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-17">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text"><a href="/wiki/Development_of_electronics_for_GM_auto_racing" title="Development of electronics for GM auto racing">Development of electronics for GM auto racing</a></span></li>
<li id="cite_note-18"><span class="mw-cite-backlink"><b><a href="#cite_ref-18">^</a></b></span> <span class="reference-text">List of Modula-2 compilers at modula2.net</span></li>
</ol>
</div>
